name: sydni
description: this is actually a portrait of my best friend!!! she is so gorgeous, we actually have matching tattoos (the honey baby is on both of our collarbones, haha) and we have our initials on our wrists too! she's the sweetest girl ever and is always so ready to make someone else feel good before even thinking about herself.. she's turning 21 next weekend and im so excited for her!!! now we can both be carded at the bar - TOGETHER!! hahaha
